title.narrative: Second Improvement to Financial Reporting and Auditing Project

description.narrative: Overall project development objectives are to: (a) build capacity to improve accuracy, comprehensiveness, reliability, and timeliness of financial and fiscal reporting at all levels of government; (b) improve public financial management, accountability, and transparency; (c) enhance the capacity of public sector managers to use credible financial information for better and informed decision-making; and (d) facilitate oversight of the use of public monies, and increase the national and international credibility of government#s financial statements and assurance processes.
